# EC2 CloudWatch Agentの設定例

```json
// /etc/cwagent/config.json
{
  "logs": {
    "logs_collected": {
      "files": {
        "collect_list": [
          {
            "file_path": "/var/log/app/application.log",
            "log_group_name": "/app/prod/api",
            "log_stream_name": "{instance_id}"
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  }
}
```

> `{instance_id}` は自動でEC2のインスタンスIDに置き換わります
